fields.description: Indicates the relative path of the error xml for the last refresh job on this particular share or container, if any. This could be a failed job or a successful job.
fields.name: ErrorManifestFile

fields.description: If a refresh job is currently in progress on this share or container, this field indicates the ARM resource ID of that job. The field is empty if no job is in progress.
fields.name: InProgressRefreshJobId

fields.description: Indicates the completed time for the last refresh job on this particular share or container, if any.This could be a failed job or a successful job.
fields.name: LastCompletedRefreshJobTimeInUTC

fields.description: Indicates the id of the last refresh job on this particular share or container,if any. This could be a failed job or a successful job.
fields.name: LastJob
